---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout title="About">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">About Mini Arcade</h1>

        <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">What is this?</h2>
            <p class="text-lg mb-4">
                Mini Arcade is my personal playground where I bring together web
                games I've built while learning and experimenting with different
                technologies and concepts.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg mb-4">
                Some games were born from online courses, while others came from
                pure curiosity ‚Äî exploring web APIs, testing design ideas, or
                simply seeing how far I can push web technologies.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Tech Stack</h2>
            <p class="text-lg mb-4">
                This site is built with <strong>Astro</strong>, <strong
                    >Tailwind CSS</strong
                >, and <strong>TypeScript</strong>. The games themselves use a
                mix of vanilla JavaScript, React, and other web technologies.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Open Source</h2>
            <p class="text-lg mb-4">
                The entire project is open source and available on GitHub. Feel
                free to check out the code, suggest improvements, or report
                bugs.
            </p>
            <a
                href="https://github.com/luismarrer/mini-arcade"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors"
            >
                View on GitHub ‚Üí
            </a>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">About Me</h2>
            <p class="text-lg mb-4">
                I'm <strong>Luis Marrero</strong>, a developer passionate about
                learning and building things üòÅ üå±.
            </p>
            <a
                href="https://luismarrer.github.io/en"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline"
            >
                Visit my portfolio ‚Üí
            </a>
        </section>
    </div>
</Layout>
